{"tid":107862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IS公然招攬作炸彈客　在港印傭淪洗腦對象","createTime":"2017-02-04T17:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T02:52:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e83d29cfd4b3573732322972d015dbdff2f7c0d6","tid":107862,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170204/bkn-20170204221040697-0204_00822_001.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170204%2Fbkn-20170204221040697-0204_00822_001.htm&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9476a91d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170204/bkn-20170204221040697-0204_00822_001.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170204/photo/bkn-20170204221040697-0204_00822_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170204%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170204221040697-0204_00822_001_01b.jpg&h=a2c304bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印尼的研究機構指出，在香港及台灣等地工作的印尼女傭，成為伊斯蘭國(IS)等回教極端組織洗腦的對象。有關注組織指出，IS招攬海外女傭為自殺式炸彈客的動作已非常公開。香港亦曾揭發有印傭派發傳單招攬同鄉加入恐怖主義活動。<br />\n<br />\n印尼是全球擁有最多回教徒的國家，該國的衝突政策研究所(IPAC)日前發表報告，指愈來愈多印尼女性透過互聯網接觸到極端主義的資訊。身在國外工作的印傭，亦是IS招攬為炸彈客的目標。印尼當局去年12月曾拘捕2名女子，指她們意圖自殺式襲擊印尼總統府，其中一人曾在台灣當外傭，相信當時被網上的極端主義資訊洗腦。<br />\n<br />\n印尼外派員工組織Migrant Care的負責人阿尼斯表示，外傭心理較脆弱，容易受毒販及原教旨極端主義的吸引。她指出：「IS現時已公然接觸外傭圈子，我們發現在香港及台灣都有此情況，被揭發的都是冰山一角。」由於這些外傭都有外匯收入，更被極端組織的男性領導人視為金礦。<br />\n<br />\n2015年3月，香港有印傭被揭在同鄉聚腳點派發宣傳單張，招攬在港工作的印傭加入伊斯蘭國，並揚言若成為成員後會派她們到內地新疆進行任務。有印傭組織透露，2年前有關招攬行動已經展開，最近更有擴展趨勢。有外傭僱主擔心，外傭被同鄉遊說下加入極端組織，恐怕會做出傷害家人的行為。"},{"pid":"0782f59679217003ac6b97a4c6734451d2494a0e","tid":107862,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:36:42.000Z","msg":"遲早發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebf60b03ba8688810b47ca5a0cea1fb82f6154a","tid":107862,"uid":51859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"正啊"},{"pid":"5ed39180d32c5144c67a2e01f9dc9c20113fe818","tid":107862,"uid":36328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb913118a620c872e3430768d5bfbbe86ea09ba","tid":107862,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:42:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母今朝搭車都見到兩個"},{"pid":"3232093783cf4115aef24220529905ffba4d7f81","tid":107862,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:43:24.000Z","msg":"如何加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f553161f4718f7fae14256153e361d510d77cb","tid":107862,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fa9482a0881d594dd650d39feb371f496d30e0","tid":107862,"uid":76879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"如果俾佢真係喺香港搞到一鑊<br />\n咁就真係港島九龍新界冇得避啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938c5d9c2ed2551f66720840cd70670156143230","tid":107862,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:52:42.000Z","msg":"香港果班差佬反恐，諗起個心都離一離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}